OL,3,C'My heart goes out to family' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister after Derry woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's Michelle O'Neill
OL,8,Fhas offered her condolences to the
OL,9,Ffamily of Amy Doherty after her death
OL,10,Fat the weekend.
OL,12,FPolice have opened a murder
OL,13,Finvestigation, and a man has been
OL,14,Farrested.
OL,16,FMichelle O'Neill said in a social
OL,17,Fmedia post: "I am deeply saddened by
OL,18,Fthe tragic news coming from Derry of
OL,19,Fthe murder of young mother of two, Amy
OL,20,FDoherty.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
