OL,3,C'My heart goes out to family' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister after Derry woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FShe continued: "In less than three
OL,8,Fweeks two more young women have lost
OL,9,Ftheir lives in heart-breaking
OL,10,Fcircumstances.
OL,12,F"Everyone must stand up and tackle the
OL,13,Fscourge of violence against women and
OL,14,Fgirls.
OL,16,F"My heart goes out to the family,
OL,17,Ffriends and community in Derry as they
OL,18,Fcome to terms with this latest
OL,19,Ftragedy."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
