OL,3,C'My heart goes out to family' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister after Derry woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FTributes have been paid to mum of two
OL,8,Fwho was aged in her 20s, after she
OL,9,Fdied in hospital on Saturday.
OL,11,FPolice are continuing to question a 30-
OL,12,Fyear-old man who has been arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,15,FDerry representatives told UTV the
OL,16,Fcommunity has been left "shocked and
OL,17,Fsaddened".
OL,26,@xD@YOU
