OL,3,C'My heart goes out to family' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister after Derry woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FPolice were called to a property in
OL,8,Fthe Summer Meadows Mews area of Derry
OL,9,Fon Saturday morning and a woman was
OL,10,Ftaken to hospital where she later died.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "Detectives from
OL,13,Fthe Police Service of Northern
OL,14,FIreland's Major Investigation Team
OL,15,Fhave launched a murder investigation
OL,16,Ffollowing the death of a woman in
OL,17,FDerry/Londonderry on Saturday, 21st
OL,18,FMarch.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
