OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774343100
OL,3,C'My heart goes out to family' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister after Derry woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Officers attended a property in the
OL,8,FSummer Meadows Mews area of the city
OL,9,Fat around 10.20 am and located an
OL,10,Finjured woman at the scene.
OL,12,F"She was taken to hospital by our
OL,13,Fcolleagues in the NIAS where she sadly
OL,14,Fdied.
OL,16,F"A 30-year-old man has been arrested
OL,17,Fon suspicion of murder.
OL,19,F"Our thoughts are with her family and
OL,20,Floved ones, who are left trying to
OL,21,Fcome to terms with this shocking loss.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
