OL,3,C'My heart goes out to family' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister after Derry woman's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Our enquiries are continuing, and I
OL,8,Fam appealing to anyone with
OL,9,Finformation, no matter how
OL,10,Finsignificant it may seem, to contact
OL,11,Four officers on 101."
